{"tid":2071580,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"九建康城項目無聲氣？","createTime":"2020-06-20T03:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T04:43:10.000Z","uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"62e58a1d9f20fe336f801a17d3bce1ddbc12c0f9","tid":2071580,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:04:05.000Z","msg":"雖然九建大家都知垃圾<br />\n但2011年已經話會有個盤<br />\n2020都無聲氣<br />\n捷和製鋼廠係咪已經拆曬？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//【本報訊】屋宇署於7月份共批出21份建築圖則，包括9項住宅及商住發展，其中規模較大的為九建（034）將軍澳石角路1至3號項目，獲批建兩幢34層高住宅，涉及518,546方呎樓面，預計提供逾1,500伙。<br />\n<br />\n上述地址位於環保大道和石角路交界，前身為捷和製鋼廠，鄰近由長實（1113）發展的峻瀅，與康城站有一街之隔。<br />\n<br />\n九建2011年已獲城規會批准興建4座42層分層住宅，提供666伙，但受近年「劏房盤」大賣影響，2016年再向城規會申請劏細，改建1,518個單位，實用面積少於431方呎的佔1,320伙，發展商2017年完成上述項目補地價，涉資約11.61億元，每方呎樓面補地價約2,238元。//"},{"pid":"0aaac802213452e1426e0059fb0c728ece4e34e2","tid":2071580,"uid":9170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"起緊啦"},{"pid":"f94778f685ef7e1b7965eb5bceb6168092e7eee1","tid":2071580,"uid":36563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T02:24:37.000Z","msg":"劏房盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d716657faf8eba7eabf0aa877d147e82b9a464f9","tid":2071580,"uid":219031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:29:18.000Z","msg":"九建質素點？"},{"pid":"935cae0929fc90650430534f0d7d8b479d32fd36","tid":2071580,"uid":258541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:35:23.000Z","msg":"其實，自己入去行下咪知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經起緊個底座"},{"pid":"f8c6fe72ff2ab08d58c328be86282bcda72b2603","tid":2071580,"uid":24697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d716657faf8eba7eabf0aa877d147e82b9a464f9","tid":2071580,"uid":219031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:29:18.000Z","msg":"九建質素點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:43:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾"}]}